{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/recipes/layout,_N_T_/recipes/[slug]/layout,_N_T_/recipes/[slug]/page,_N_T_/recipes/classic-margherita-pizza"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/recipes/$d$slug/__PAGE__","/recipes/$d$slug","/recipes","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"inter_7b064e0d-module__MOT0tq__variable playfair_display_d5eda251-module__JGL7aG__variable h-full antialiased\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/2a65768255d6b625-s.p.3u4lli0-axodc.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/83afe278b6a6bb3c-s.p.2bn3s6zvc0dyp.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0sr-6vwes3bgx.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0_a3f2s3xcdlr.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3tqnqxx00iegt.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3vxefajc32xya.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/2b5ld3b690ufj.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-0f7e8t6an3_x0.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/2l23laejyscle.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0i31m7nnsmowg.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1at72y-usxqm1.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Classic Margherita Pizza | Appropriated Kitchen</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"A simple, authentic Margherita pizza with fresh mozzarella, basil, and San Marzano tomatoes. This Neapolitan classic proves that the best food comes from the best ingredients, not complicated techniques.\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Classic Margherita Pizza\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"A simple, authentic Margherita pizza with fresh mozzarella, basil, and San Marzano tomatoes. This Neapolitan classic proves that the best food comes from the best ingredients, not complicated techniques.\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://appropriatedkitchen.com/images/recipes/margherita-pizza.jpg\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\"/><meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2026-06-13\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Classic Margherita Pizza\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"A simple, authentic Margherita pizza with fresh mozzarella, basil, and San Marzano tomatoes. This Neapolitan classic proves that the best food comes from the best ingredients, not complicated techniques.\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://appropriatedkitchen.com/images/recipes/margherita-pizza.jpg\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script>\n              (function() {\n                try {\n                  var theme = localStorage.getItem('theme');\n                  if (theme === 'dark' || (!theme && window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)) {\n                    document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');\n                  }\n                } catch(e) {}\n              })();\n            </script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-30 w-full border-b bg-background/95 backdrop-blur supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-background/60\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-16 max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent font-serif\">Appropriated Kitchen</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-8\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors\" href=\"/recipes\">Recipes</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors\" href=\"/about\">About</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"hidden md:block\"><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" aria-label=\"Switch to dark mode\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:not-aria-[haspopup]:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground aria-expanded:bg-muted aria-expanded:text-foreground dark:hover:bg-muted/50 size-8 theme-toggle\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"md:hidden\"><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:not-aria-[haspopup]:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground aria-expanded:bg-muted aria-expanded:text-foreground dark:hover:bg-muted/50 size-8 mobile-nav\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"aspect-[2/1] w-full rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chef-hat h-20 w-20 text-muted-foreground/40\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M17 21a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-5.35c0-.457.316-.844.727-1.041a4 4 0 0 0-2.134-7.589 5 5 0 0 0-9.186 0 4 4 0 0 0-2.134 7.588c.411.198.727.585.727 1.041V20a1 1 0 0 0 1 1Z\"></path><path d=\"M6 17h12\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold font-serif sm:text-5xl\">Classic Margherita Pizza</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground\">A simple, authentic Margherita pizza with fresh mozzarella, basil, and San Marzano tomatoes. This Neapolitan classic proves that the best food comes from the best ingredients, not complicated techniques.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg><span>Prep: <!-- -->20 min</span></div><span class=\"text-border\">|</span><span>Cook: <!-- -->12 min</span><span class=\"text-border\">|</span><span>Total: <!-- -->32 min</span><span class=\"text-border\">|</span><span>Serves <!-- -->4</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" data-variant=\"default\" class=\"group/badge inline-flex h-5 w-fit shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1 overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border border-transparent px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50 has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-1.5 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-1.5 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3! bg-primary text-primary-foreground [a]:hover:bg-primary/80\">easy</span><span data-slot=\"badge\" data-variant=\"secondary\" class=\"group/badge inline-flex h-5 w-fit shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1 overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border border-transparent px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50 has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-1.5 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-1.5 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3! bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground [a]:hover:bg-secondary/80\">italian</span><span data-slot=\"badge\" data-variant=\"secondary\" class=\"group/badge inline-flex h-5 w-fit shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1 overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border border-transparent px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50 has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-1.5 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-1.5 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3! bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground [a]:hover:bg-secondary/80\">pizza</span><span data-slot=\"badge\" data-variant=\"secondary\" class=\"group/badge inline-flex h-5 w-fit shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1 overflow-hidden rounded-4xl border border-transparent px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50 has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-1.5 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-1.5 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3! bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground [a]:hover:bg-secondary/80\">vegetarian</span></div><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" aria-label=\"Print recipe\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:not-aria-[haspopup]:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 border-border bg-background hover:bg-muted hover:text-foreground aria-expanded:bg-muted aria-expanded:text-foreground dark:border-input dark:bg-input/30 dark:hover:bg-input/50 h-8 px-2.5 has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-2 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-2 gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-printer h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 18H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v5a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 9V3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h10a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v6\"></path><rect x=\"6\" y=\"14\" width=\"12\" height=\"8\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg>Print Recipe</button></div></div></div><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><div class=\"grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1fr_280px]\"><div class=\"space-y-10\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold font-serif\">Ingredients</h2><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-medium\">2 ¼ tsp</strong> <!-- -->active dry yeast</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-medium\">1 cup</strong> <!-- -->warm water</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-medium\">3 cups</strong> <!-- -->all-purpose flour</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-medium\">2 tbsp</strong> <!-- -->olive oil</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-medium\">1 tsp</strong> <!-- -->salt</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-medium\">½ cup</strong> <!-- -->San Marzano tomato sauce</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-medium\">8 oz</strong> <!-- -->fresh mozzarella<span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\"> — <!-- -->sliced</span></span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-medium\">¼ cup</strong> <!-- -->fresh basil leaves</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-base\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary\"></span><span> <!-- -->semolina flour<span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\"> — <!-- -->for dusting</span></span></li></ul></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold font-serif\">Instructions</h2><div class=\"prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:font-serif prose-headings:text-xl prose-headings:mt-8 prose-headings:mb-3 prose-li:marker:text-primary\"><p>This is the pizza that started it all for me. The first time I had a real Margherita in Naples, I understood what all the fuss was about — and I&#x27;ve been chasing that perfect bite ever since.</p>\n<h2>Tips for Success</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Use a pizza stone or steel</strong> if you have one. Preheat it in the oven for at least 30 minutes at the highest temperature your oven can go.</li>\n<li><strong>Don&#x27;t overload the toppings.</strong> A true Margherita is about balance — a little sauce, a little cheese, a few basil leaves.</li>\n<li><strong>Wet mozzarella is the enemy.</strong> Pat your fresh mozzarella dry with paper towels before slicing, or you&#x27;ll end up with a soggy crust.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Instructions</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Activate the yeast.</strong> In a small bowl, combine warm water (110°F / 43°C) and yeast. Let sit for 5 minutes until foamy.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Make the dough.</strong> In a large bowl, combine flour and salt. Add the yeast mixture and olive oil. Mix until a shaggy dough forms.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Knead.</strong> Turn dough onto a floured surface and knead for 8-10 minutes until smooth and elastic. The dough should spring back when poked.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>First rise.</strong> Place dough in an oiled bowl, cover with plastic wrap, and let rise in a warm spot for 1-2 hours until doubled in size.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Shape.</strong> Divide dough into 4 equal balls. On a semolina-dusted surface, stretch each ball into a 10-inch round. Use your hands — don&#x27;t use a rolling pin, which deflates the bubbles.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Preheat.</strong> Place a pizza stone or inverted baking sheet in the oven and preheat to 500°F (260°C) or the highest setting for at least 30 minutes.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Assemble.</strong> Spread a thin layer of tomato sauce on each dough round. Tear mozzarella pieces and distribute evenly.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Bake.</strong> Slide pizzas onto the hot stone (one at a time) and bake for 8-12 minutes until the crust is golden and the cheese is bubbling.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Finish.</strong> Remove from oven, top with fresh basil leaves, drizzle with a little olive oil, and serve immediately.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Enjoy your taste of Naples!</p></div></div></div><aside class=\"md:sticky md:top-24 self-start\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border bg-card p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold font-serif mb-4\">Nutrition</h2><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-4\">Per serving</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3 text-center\"><div class=\"text-lg font-bold\">285</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Calories</div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3 text-center\"><div class=\"text-lg font-bold\">12g</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Protein</div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3 text-center\"><div class=\"text-lg font-bold\">36g</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Carbs</div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3 text-center\"><div class=\"text-lg font-bold\">10g</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Fat</div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3 text-center\"><div class=\"text-lg font-bold\">2g</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Fiber</div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3 text-center\"><div class=\"text-lg font-bold\">520mg</div><div class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Sodium</div></div></div></div></aside></div><div class=\"print-recipe-card print-only hidden print:block\"><div class=\"text-center mb-6\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-bold font-serif\">Appropriated Kitchen</h2><p class=\"text-sm italic text-muted-foreground\">Your Food, My Way</p></div><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold font-serif\">Classic Margherita Pizza</h1><p class=\"text-sm mt-1\">Prep: <!-- -->20 min<!-- --> | Cook: <!-- -->12 min<!-- --> | Total: <!-- -->32 min<!-- --> | Serves: <!-- -->4</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2\">Ingredients</h3><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm\"><li><strong>2 ¼ tsp</strong> <!-- -->active dry yeast</li><li><strong>1 cup</strong> <!-- -->warm water</li><li><strong>3 cups</strong> <!-- -->all-purpose flour</li><li><strong>2 tbsp</strong> <!-- -->olive oil</li><li><strong>1 tsp</strong> <!-- -->salt</li><li><strong>½ cup</strong> <!-- -->San Marzano tomato sauce</li><li><strong>8 oz</strong> <!-- -->fresh mozzarella<span class=\"text-gray-500\"> — <!-- -->sliced</span></li><li><strong>¼ cup</strong> <!-- -->fresh basil leaves</li><li> <!-- -->semolina flour<span class=\"text-gray-500\"> — <!-- -->for dusting</span></li></ul><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2\">Instructions</h3><div class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line\">\nThis is the pizza that started it all for me. The first time I had a real Margherita in Naples, I understood what all the fuss was about — and I&#x27;ve been chasing that perfect bite ever since.\n\n## Tips for Success\n\n- **Use a pizza stone or steel** if you have one. Preheat it in the oven for at least 30 minutes at the highest temperature your oven can go.\n- **Don&#x27;t overload the toppings.** A true Margherita is about balance — a little sauce, a little cheese, a few basil leaves.\n- **Wet mozzarella is the enemy.** Pat your fresh mozzarella dry with paper towels before slicing, or you&#x27;ll end up with a soggy crust.\n\n## Instructions\n\n1. **Activate the yeast.** In a small bowl, combine warm water (110°F / 43°C) and yeast. Let sit for 5 minutes until foamy.\n\n2. **Make the dough.** In a large bowl, combine flour and salt. Add the yeast mixture and olive oil. Mix until a shaggy dough forms.\n\n3. **Knead.** Turn dough onto a floured surface and knead for 8-10 minutes until smooth and elastic. The dough should spring back when poked.\n\n4. **First rise.** Place dough in an oiled bowl, cover with plastic wrap, and let rise in a warm spot for 1-2 hours until doubled in size.\n\n5. **Shape.** Divide dough into 4 equal balls. On a semolina-dusted surface, stretch each ball into a 10-inch round. Use your hands — don&#x27;t use a rolling pin, which deflates the bubbles.\n\n6. **Preheat.** Place a pizza stone or inverted baking sheet in the oven and preheat to 500°F (260°C) or the highest setting for at least 30 minutes.\n\n7. **Assemble.** Spread a thin layer of tomato sauce on each dough round. Tear mozzarella pieces and distribute evenly.\n\n8. **Bake.** Slide pizzas onto the hot stone (one at a time) and bake for 8-12 minutes until the crust is golden and the cheese is bubbling.\n\n9. **Finish.** Remove from oven, top with fresh basil leaves, drizzle with a little olive oil, and serve immediately.\n\nEnjoy your taste of Naples!\n</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mt-6 mb-2\">Nutrition Per Serving</h3><table class=\"text-sm w-full max-w-xs\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"font-medium\">Calories</td><td>285</td></tr><tr><td class=\"font-medium\">Protein</td><td>12g</td></tr><tr><td class=\"font-medium\">Carbs</td><td>36g</td></tr><tr><td class=\"font-medium\">Fat</td><td>10g</td></tr><tr><td class=\"font-medium\">Fiber</td><td>2g</td></tr><tr><td class=\"font-medium\">Sodium</td><td>520mg</td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"print-url\">https://appropriatedkitchen.com</div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t bg-muted/30\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><a class=\"text-lg font-bold font-serif\" href=\"/\">Appropriated Kitchen</a><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground italic\">Your Food, My Way</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/appropriatedkitchen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"Instagram\" class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.